LAGOS – Popular Nigerian Disc Jockey, Producer, & Philanthropist, Florence Ifeoluwa Otedola, a.k.a DJ Cuppy has shared her opinion on self love. According to the sensational female DJ who recently shaved her hair, contrary to popular opinion, expressing profound love for one’s self is not selfishness. DJ Cuppy made this statement on her verified twitter handle, @cuppymusic. Troops Of Operation Safe Haven Rescue Three Kidnapped Students Provision Of Health Insurance To Pensioners, Our Priority… She wrote, “Self love isn’t selfishness”. See tweet below; Self Love isn’t Selfishness  #CuppyDat pic.twitter.com/l0N5TZ1Rj6